      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AMAZING MOLLY (4) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at this track over 527m behind Zipping Desire (31.58) in a Mix. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Better than last start and worth following up. SWIFT HANK (8) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten one length (19.82) behind Train Of Thought at this track. Will give a great sight again. FANTASTIC ELLE (3) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing nine from 17 starts. Finished in the minors latest when third (25.33) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Has a good record at this journey. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Winning chance. TRALEE JOEY (1) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
